{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/Study/ml/3/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Tinnia Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"3cea7a00-1c6b-5530-bef4-285a0ec2f56d","excerpt":"Matplotlib 특징 Python의 시각화 도구 사용 함수 기본 xlabel, ylabel color linestyle title legend = 범례 grid xylim = xy축 범위 설정 scatter(점 그래프) bar histogram(히스토그램) boxplot…","html":"<h3>Matplotlib</h3>\n<h5>특징</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Python의 시각화 도구</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<h5>사용</h5>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"python\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> matplotlib.pyplot </span><span class=\"mtk11\">as</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> plt</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\"># 보통 plt라는 별칭으로 호출</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<br />\n<h5>함수</h5>\n<h6>기본</h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"python\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">X </span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">range</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk3\">100</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">Y </span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">range</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk3\">100</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.plot(X, Y)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.show()</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h6>xlabel, ylabel</h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"python\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.xlabel(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;X values&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.ylabel(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;Y values&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h6>color</h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"python\" data-index=\"3\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.plot(X, Y, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">color</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;#ff0022&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h6>linestyle</h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"python\" data-index=\"4\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.plot(X, Y, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">ls</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;dashed&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk4\"># line 모양</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.plot(x, y, </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;m:&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">linewidth</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk3\">9</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)\t</span><span class=\"mtk4\"># line 두께</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h6>title</h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"python\" data-index=\"5\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.title(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;Title&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h6>legend = 범례</h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"python\" data-index=\"6\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.plot(X1, Y1, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">label</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;line1&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.plot(X2, Y2, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">label</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;line2&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.legend(</span><span class=\"mtk3\">shadow</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk7\">True</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">fancybox</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk7\">True</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">loc</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;lower right&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h6>grid</h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"python\" data-index=\"7\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.grid(</span><span class=\"mtk7\">True</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">lw</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk3\">0.4</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">ls</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;--&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">c</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;.90&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h6>xylim = xy축 범위 설정</h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"python\" data-index=\"8\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.xlim(</span><span class=\"mtk15\">-</span><span class=\"mtk3\">100</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span><span class=\"mtk3\">100</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.ylim(</span><span class=\"mtk15\">-</span><span class=\"mtk3\">100</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span><span class=\"mtk3\">100</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h6>scatter(점 그래프)</h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"python\" data-index=\"9\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.scatter(data1[:,</span><span class=\"mtk3\">0</span><span class=\"mtk1\">], data1[:,</span><span class=\"mtk3\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">], </span><span class=\"mtk3\">s</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\">area, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">c</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;b&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">marker</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;x&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)\t</span><span class=\"mtk4\"># s로 데이터 크기 지정, marker로 모양 지정</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h6>bar</h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"python\" data-index=\"10\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.bar(X, Y, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">width</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk3\">0.5</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h6>histogram(히스토그램)</h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"python\" data-index=\"11\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.hist(X, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">bins</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk3\">100</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">alpha</span><span class=\"mtk15\">=</span><span class=\"mtk3\">0.3</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)\t</span><span class=\"mtk4\"># bins로 bar 개수 조정 / alpha 로 투명도 조절</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h6>boxplot</h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"python\" data-index=\"12\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.boxplot(data)</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h6>subplot</h6>\n<ul>\n<li>여러 그래프 출력</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"python\" data-index=\"13\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.subplot(</span><span class=\"mtk3\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.plot(x, y, </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;r&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.subplot(</span><span class=\"mtk3\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.plot(x, y, </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;g&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.subplot(</span><span class=\"mtk3\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">3</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.plot(y, x, </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;k&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.subplot(</span><span class=\"mtk3\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk3\">4</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">plt.plot(x, np.exp(x), </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;b&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: n